object.customQuery:
SELECT note.SystemId AS system_id,
ParentId AS parent_id,
note.CMMContainer AS cmm_container,
Id AS id,
UpdateCount AS update_count,
UpdateUser AS update_user,
UpdateTimestamp AS update_timestamp,
TemplateId AS template_id,
IdRef AS id_ref,
Description AS description,
PriorityCd AS priority_cd,
Category AS category,
Memo AS memo,
StickyInd AS sticky_ind,
Comments AS comments,
Status AS status,
note.AddDt AS add_dt,
note.AddTm AS add_tm,
AddUser AS add_user,
UpdateDt AS update_dt,
UpdateTm AS update_tm,
SourceRef AS source_ref,
TransactionNumber AS transaction_number,
SourceContainerName AS source_container_name,
ShowOnAllProducerContainersInd AS show_on_all_producer_containers_ind,
RowId AS row_id
FROM
 note 
where note.CmmContainer in ('Policy','Claim','Application')
